1
00:01:16,640 --> 00:01:17,700
We brought you here

2
00:01:18,080 --> 00:01:19,320
to ask some questions.

3
00:01:19,320 --> 00:01:20,920
You must answer truthfully.

4
00:01:26,000 --> 00:01:27,640
Something happened to Lu Yang.

5
00:01:27,640 --> 00:01:28,080
He...

6
00:01:29,000 --> 00:01:30,200
What happened to him?

7
00:01:31,760 --> 00:01:32,620
Lu Yang is dead.

8
00:01:35,560 --> 00:01:36,080
He...

9
00:01:38,120 --> 00:01:39,160
He's dead.

10
00:01:44,039 --> 00:01:45,320
How could he die?

11
00:01:50,479 --> 00:01:52,340
Come back to our hometown with me.

12
00:01:52,759 --> 00:01:54,820
Sure. What do you want to do back home?

13
00:01:55,640 --> 00:01:57,120
I can work

14
00:01:57,560 --> 00:01:58,890
in an engineering team,

15
00:02:00,280 --> 00:02:01,240
and I

16
00:02:02,920 --> 00:02:04,250
might become a teacher.

17
00:02:36,800 --> 00:02:38,240
Who did you offend?

18
00:02:39,920 --> 00:02:41,000
How could you die?

19
00:02:51,920 --> 00:02:53,800
The portrait we got from Old Deng,

20
00:02:54,120 --> 00:02:55,360
after image comparison,

21
00:02:55,360 --> 00:02:57,240
has a very high overlap rate

22
00:02:57,360 --> 00:02:59,560
with the surveillance video at the scene.

23
00:02:59,560 --> 00:03:01,160
The on-site trace inspection

24
00:03:01,160 --> 00:03:02,800
did not find any

25
00:03:02,800 --> 00:03:03,960
DNA residue.

26
00:03:04,720 --> 00:03:07,760
The more I hear this, the more it sounds like a hired killing.

27
00:03:07,760 --> 00:03:09,160
Combining the two cases,

28
00:03:09,160 --> 00:03:10,400
Lu Yang knew Tian Liang and Xia Lin

29
00:03:10,400 --> 00:03:12,130
had an improper relationship.

30
00:03:12,720 --> 00:03:14,920
So Lu Yang used this to threaten Xia Lin.

31
00:03:15,800 --> 00:03:16,600
Coincidentally,

32
00:03:16,600 --> 00:03:19,160
right after we questioned Xia Lin and Huang Xiaoyun,

33
00:03:19,160 --> 00:03:20,490
Lu Yang had an accident.

34
00:03:20,920 --> 00:03:23,450
We must investigate if this is a coincidence.

35
00:03:23,880 --> 00:03:25,280
We can't find the person,

36
00:03:25,720 --> 00:03:27,579
and the license plate is blocked.

37
00:03:28,160 --> 00:03:29,820
Then look for the tire tracks.

38
00:03:52,760 --> 00:03:53,520
Are you blind?

39
00:03:53,520 --> 00:03:54,280
What are you doing? Right?

40
00:03:54,280 --> 00:03:55,480
Sorry, sorry, sorry.

41
00:03:55,680 --> 00:03:56,360
What's wrong with you?

42
00:03:56,360 --> 00:03:57,000
What are you doing?

43
00:03:57,000 --> 00:03:58,440
I saw everything, you hit him.

44
00:03:58,440 --> 00:03:59,400
Did you do it on purpose?

45
00:03:59,400 --> 00:04:00,000
What are you talking about?

46
00:04:00,000 --> 00:04:00,400
Sorry,

47
00:04:00,440 --> 00:04:01,080
brother.

48
00:04:01,160 --> 00:04:02,360
Tell me what you want.

49
00:04:02,400 --> 00:04:03,720
I'm in a good mood today.

50
00:04:03,720 --> 00:04:05,180
Take your car and get lost.

51
00:04:05,440 --> 00:04:06,520
Okay, sorry.

52
00:04:09,680 --> 00:04:10,520
What's wrong with this person?

53
00:04:10,520 --> 00:04:11,160
Alright, stop talking.

54
00:04:11,160 --> 00:04:11,760
Let's go.

55
00:04:22,600 --> 00:04:23,080
Ms. Xia,

56
00:04:23,480 --> 00:04:24,120
sorry to bother you.

57
00:04:24,120 --> 00:04:24,920
Sorry to bother you.

58
00:04:24,920 --> 00:04:25,850
Why are you here?

59
00:04:26,800 --> 00:04:27,280
Well,

60
00:04:27,360 --> 00:04:29,690
we have a few questions to verify with you.

61
00:04:29,760 --> 00:04:31,290
Haven't you already asked?

62
00:04:31,360 --> 00:04:32,400
They are a few new questions.

63
00:04:32,400 --> 00:04:33,159
Don't worry.

64
00:04:34,120 --> 00:04:34,760
Is it convenient to tell us

65
00:04:34,760 --> 00:04:36,490
what you were doing last night?

66
00:04:36,920 --> 00:04:38,480
I went home after work last night.

67
00:04:38,480 --> 00:04:39,680
I didn't go anywhere.

68
00:04:39,760 --> 00:04:41,020
Do you have witnesses?

69
00:04:41,120 --> 00:04:42,050
What do you mean?

70
00:04:43,200 --> 00:04:44,120
Nothing else,

71
00:04:44,400 --> 00:04:46,800
just a normal inquiry for related persons.

72
00:04:47,560 --> 00:04:50,080
The surveillance camera recorded me going home.

73
00:04:50,080 --> 00:04:52,040
And at night, Xiaoyun, Qiming, and I

74
00:04:52,040 --> 00:04:52,920
all ate at home.

75
00:04:56,040 --> 00:04:57,440
Did Ye Qiming go out again?

76
00:04:57,440 --> 00:04:57,880
No.

77
00:04:58,320 --> 00:04:59,440
We went to sleep after dinner,

78
00:04:59,440 --> 00:05:00,170
quite early.

79
00:05:01,440 --> 00:05:02,640
Then we won't bother you anymore today,

80
00:05:02,640 --> 00:05:03,100
Ms. Xia.

81
00:05:03,440 --> 00:05:04,040
Thank you.

82
00:05:04,200 --> 00:05:04,760
Thank you.

83
00:05:04,760 --> 00:05:05,160
Okay.

84
00:05:22,080 --> 00:05:22,560
Mr. Ye.

85
00:05:23,600 --> 00:05:24,730
What a coincidence.

86
00:05:25,040 --> 00:05:26,080
We just came from your house

87
00:05:26,080 --> 00:05:26,440
Yes.

88
00:05:26,720 --> 00:05:28,040
to ask you a few questions,

89
00:05:28,040 --> 00:05:29,300
and we ran into Ms. Xia.

90
00:05:29,400 --> 00:05:29,960
She said

91
00:05:30,400 --> 00:05:32,120
you were at home all night yesterday.

92
00:05:32,120 --> 00:05:32,850
I was at home.

93
00:05:33,840 --> 00:05:34,600
It's nothing serious.

94
00:05:34,600 --> 00:05:36,260
Just some routine questions.

95
00:05:36,920 --> 00:05:37,760
You've had a long day.

96
00:05:37,760 --> 00:05:39,290
You can go back and rest now.

97
00:05:39,840 --> 00:05:40,360
Okay.

98
00:05:40,480 --> 00:05:41,080
Thanks for your hard work.

99
00:05:41,080 --> 00:05:42,880
Contact me if you need anything.

100
00:05:49,920 --> 00:05:50,720
Any thoughts?

101
00:05:51,560 --> 00:05:52,240
Not really.

102
00:05:52,760 --> 00:05:53,690
I just feel that,

103
00:05:54,760 --> 00:05:56,960
after all, it's a matter of life and death.

104
00:05:56,960 --> 00:05:58,600
Not nervous, nor excited.

105
00:05:59,320 --> 00:06:00,520
He is a bit too calm.

106
00:06:01,360 --> 00:06:01,840
Indeed.

107
00:06:02,400 --> 00:06:03,120
Looking at it this way,

108
00:06:03,120 --> 00:06:05,180
Xia Lin's reaction is the normal one.

109
00:06:05,640 --> 00:06:07,240
Not many people know Lu Yang.

110
00:06:07,760 --> 00:06:08,690
He is one of them.

111
00:06:09,880 --> 00:06:10,410
Alright.

112
00:06:10,560 --> 00:06:11,090
Let's go.

113
00:06:33,400 --> 00:06:34,800
Yuna, Yuna.

114
00:06:36,680 --> 00:06:37,480
What's wrong?

115
00:06:37,800 --> 00:06:39,330
The project funds are gone.

116
00:06:40,240 --> 00:06:40,800
Qiming.

117
00:06:41,760 --> 00:06:42,159
Here,

118
00:06:42,400 --> 00:06:45,400
try the apples I bought today and see if they're sweet.

119
00:06:45,880 --> 00:06:46,680
What's wrong?

120
00:06:46,760 --> 00:06:48,020
You don't look so good.

121
00:06:48,440 --> 00:06:49,700
Did something happen?

122
00:06:49,840 --> 00:06:52,000
The over one million in relocation funds for the farmers,

123
00:06:52,000 --> 00:06:52,920
I lost it.

124
00:06:54,680 --> 00:06:55,280
What?

125
00:06:55,800 --> 00:06:57,530
The relocation funds are gone?

126
00:06:57,800 --> 00:06:59,040
How could this happen?

127
00:06:59,040 --> 00:07:00,370
Did you call the police?

128
00:07:00,520 --> 00:07:01,320
I already did.

129
00:07:02,440 --> 00:07:04,240
But when we'll get the money back

130
00:07:04,520 --> 00:07:05,320
is hard to say.

131
00:07:07,120 --> 00:07:08,320
That's so much money.

132
00:07:08,680 --> 00:07:11,010
If it can't be given to the farmers in time,

133
00:07:11,200 --> 00:07:12,800
what will they do?

134
00:07:13,320 --> 00:07:14,760
The money owed to the farmers

135
00:07:14,760 --> 00:07:16,620
can't be returned to them in time.

136
00:07:16,680 --> 00:07:17,000
Well,

137
00:07:17,000 --> 00:07:17,730
don't worry.

138
00:07:18,200 --> 00:07:19,730
I'll cover the money first.

139
00:07:20,000 --> 00:07:20,930
You'll cover it?

140
00:07:22,120 --> 00:07:23,380
That's over a million.

141
00:07:25,280 --> 00:07:26,000
I... I...

142
00:07:26,440 --> 00:07:29,370
No wonder my right eyelid has been twitching lately.

143
00:07:30,200 --> 00:07:31,530
Did you offend someone?

144
00:07:31,840 --> 00:07:33,900
Someone might be trying to set you up.

145
00:07:35,560 --> 00:07:36,890
It's really hard to say.

146
00:07:37,880 --> 00:07:38,400
But,

147
00:07:39,280 --> 00:07:40,680
I'll figure it out.

148
00:07:47,000 --> 00:07:48,159
It wasn't money in the bag.

149
00:07:48,159 --> 00:07:48,680
What?

150
00:07:49,600 --> 00:07:50,460
It was swapped.

151
00:07:50,920 --> 00:07:51,850
What do we do now?

152
00:07:52,560 --> 00:07:54,220
Let's leave it at that for now.

153
00:07:58,640 --> 00:08:01,360
Did Ye Qiming plan this,

154
00:08:01,880 --> 00:08:03,160
or is he in the dark too?

155
00:08:05,880 --> 00:08:06,440
Xiaoyun.

156
00:08:07,360 --> 00:08:07,960
Xiaoyun.

157
00:08:08,680 --> 00:08:10,360
Look, I bought winter melon and ribs.

158
00:08:10,360 --> 00:08:11,480
We'll have winter melon and rib soup tonight.

159
00:08:11,480 --> 00:08:12,320
Wash the vegetables.

160
00:08:12,320 --> 00:08:12,680
Okay.

161
00:08:17,800 --> 00:08:18,330
Xiaoyun.

162
00:08:18,560 --> 00:08:19,090
Xiaoyun.

163
00:08:20,920 --> 00:08:22,050
Where are you going?

164
00:08:22,280 --> 00:08:23,140
Wash them here.

165
00:08:27,800 --> 00:08:28,600
What's wrong?

166
00:08:31,040 --> 00:08:32,480
What's wrong with you?

167
00:08:33,840 --> 00:08:34,360
Lu Yang

168
00:08:36,440 --> 00:08:37,039
is dead.

169
00:08:37,720 --> 00:08:38,650
What did you say?

170
00:08:39,240 --> 00:08:40,120
Lu Yang is dead.

171
00:08:40,640 --> 00:08:41,440
How did he die?

172
00:08:42,159 --> 00:08:43,280
The police told me

173
00:08:44,520 --> 00:08:46,360
he died in a homestay apartment

174
00:08:47,240 --> 00:08:48,370
from gas poisoning.

175
00:08:50,160 --> 00:08:51,420
How could this happen?

176
00:08:52,120 --> 00:08:54,650
Was it an accident, or did someone murder him?

177
00:08:55,200 --> 00:08:55,960
I don't know.

178
00:08:57,360 --> 00:08:58,620
I don't know anything.

179
00:09:01,680 --> 00:09:02,410
Don't worry.

180
00:09:02,640 --> 00:09:03,720
The police are on it.

181
00:09:03,720 --> 00:09:05,320
They will find out the truth.

182
00:09:06,080 --> 00:09:06,680
Auntie,

183
00:09:07,520 --> 00:09:10,050
I want to go back to my room and rest for a while.

184
00:09:10,280 --> 00:09:10,840
Go ahead.

185
00:09:44,320 --> 00:09:45,920
Lu Yang is dead. Did you know?

186
00:09:48,320 --> 00:09:50,240
What did you say? Lu Yang is dead?

187
00:09:51,360 --> 00:09:51,880
When?

188
00:09:52,920 --> 00:09:53,720
How did he die?

189
00:09:55,880 --> 00:09:56,680
Xiaoyun said

190
00:09:57,360 --> 00:09:59,160
it was carbon monoxide poisoning.

191
00:09:59,160 --> 00:10:00,080
This kid,

192
00:10:00,840 --> 00:10:02,370
how could he be so careless?

193
00:10:02,960 --> 00:10:04,720
That's why I say girls looking for a partner

194
00:10:04,720 --> 00:10:05,650
must be careful.

195
00:10:05,880 --> 00:10:06,680
Actually, I think Lu Yang's case,

196
00:10:06,680 --> 00:10:08,320
whether it's suicide or murder,

197
00:10:08,320 --> 00:10:09,320
must be related to

198
00:10:09,440 --> 00:10:10,720
his usual bad deeds

199
00:10:10,960 --> 00:10:12,040
and misbehavior.

200
00:10:14,800 --> 00:10:16,600
How do you know he did bad things?

201
00:10:17,240 --> 00:10:17,720
I...

202
00:10:18,840 --> 00:10:20,000
I was just guessing.

203
00:10:23,520 --> 00:10:25,760
Xiaoyun is in a very bad mood lately.

204
00:10:26,240 --> 00:10:27,400
I already tried to comfort her,

205
00:10:27,400 --> 00:10:28,320
but she wouldn't listen.

206
00:10:28,320 --> 00:10:29,720
Why don't you try talking to her?

207
00:10:29,720 --> 00:10:30,200
Okay.

208
00:10:53,320 --> 00:10:54,320
About Lu Yang...

209
00:10:56,040 --> 00:10:57,520
He didn't study hard

210
00:10:58,000 --> 00:11:00,130
and often went to bars and nightclubs,

211
00:11:00,200 --> 00:11:01,130
messing around.

212
00:11:01,840 --> 00:11:03,500
The point is, he made enemies.

213
00:11:04,040 --> 00:11:05,480
What happened to him today

214
00:11:05,480 --> 00:11:06,840
is his own fault.

215
00:11:07,440 --> 00:11:08,680
There's no need for you

216
00:11:08,680 --> 00:11:09,810
to be too sad for him,

217
00:11:10,120 --> 00:11:10,520
okay?

218
00:11:10,840 --> 00:11:12,770
But where did he get all this money?

219
00:11:13,680 --> 00:11:15,000
People change.

220
00:11:16,080 --> 00:11:17,560
His usual consumption records

221
00:11:17,560 --> 00:11:18,820
can be easily checked.

222
00:11:19,360 --> 00:11:20,820
You are just too innocent,

223
00:11:21,080 --> 00:11:23,080
and he kept you in the dark all along.

224
00:11:23,640 --> 00:11:25,370
But even if he did those things,

225
00:11:25,840 --> 00:11:27,320
he didn't have to die.

226
00:11:32,000 --> 00:11:33,260
Xiaoyun, don't be sad.

227
00:11:33,800 --> 00:11:34,600
I promise you,

228
00:11:35,040 --> 00:11:36,760
I'll look into this matter for you,

229
00:11:36,760 --> 00:11:37,320
alright?

230
00:11:38,600 --> 00:11:39,600
Thank you, Uncle.

231
00:11:40,680 --> 00:11:42,480
Don't be sad. I'll get going now.

232
00:11:49,880 --> 00:11:50,480
Come here.

233
00:11:55,800 --> 00:11:58,560
You just said you'd help Xiaoyun figure this out.

234
00:11:59,720 --> 00:12:00,760
How are you going to do that?

235
00:12:00,760 --> 00:12:02,480
Does Lu Yang's death have anything to do with you?

236
00:12:02,480 --> 00:12:03,680
Don't talk nonsense.

237
00:12:04,040 --> 00:12:05,320
You need evidence to back up your words.

238
00:12:05,320 --> 00:12:05,960
Ye Qiming.

239
00:12:06,880 --> 00:12:07,960
I know you too well.

240
00:12:08,400 --> 00:12:09,520
If I didn't have proof,

241
00:12:09,520 --> 00:12:11,050
I wouldn't say such things.

242
00:12:11,240 --> 00:12:12,920
Are you saying I'm a murderer?

243
00:12:13,240 --> 00:12:14,800
A highly educated intellectual

244
00:12:14,800 --> 00:12:16,200
marrying a murderer.

245
00:12:16,640 --> 00:12:18,080
Don't you think that's ridiculous?

246
00:12:18,080 --> 00:12:20,320
Then why did you marry me in the first place?

247
00:12:20,320 --> 00:12:21,200
I married you back then

248
00:12:21,200 --> 00:12:23,360
because I was blind and misjudged you.

249
00:12:26,400 --> 00:12:28,880
It's not just your family who looks down on me.

250
00:12:28,880 --> 00:12:30,080
Actually, deep down,

251
00:12:30,640 --> 00:12:33,300
you've always looked down on me all these years.

252
00:12:33,360 --> 00:12:34,880
If I looked down on you,

253
00:12:35,200 --> 00:12:36,880
I wouldn't have gone against everyone's objections

254
00:12:36,880 --> 00:12:38,140
to marry you back then.

255
00:12:39,440 --> 00:12:40,440
Now I even suspect

256
00:12:40,680 --> 00:12:42,080
that the thugs I encountered while sketching

257
00:12:42,080 --> 00:12:43,520
were arranged by you.

258
00:12:44,480 --> 00:12:45,760
A city lady

259
00:12:46,640 --> 00:12:48,100
is nothing more than this.

260
00:12:48,360 --> 00:12:50,400
You are simply hopeless.

261
00:12:50,560 --> 00:12:51,400
I'm hopeless?

262
00:12:51,840 --> 00:12:52,960
Is it my problem?

263
00:12:53,360 --> 00:12:54,890
It's clearly your problem.

264
00:12:56,120 --> 00:12:56,760
Ye Qiming.

265
00:12:57,440 --> 00:12:58,770
I think you just got rich

266
00:12:58,920 --> 00:13:00,380
and want to dump me, right?

267
00:13:00,600 --> 00:13:01,330
Don't worry.

268
00:13:02,160 --> 00:13:03,360
I could never dump

269
00:13:03,480 --> 00:13:05,600
the arrogant Miss Xia Lin.

270
00:13:05,840 --> 00:13:08,080
I'm just giving someone a taste

271
00:13:09,000 --> 00:13:10,280
of their own medicine.

272
00:13:12,760 --> 00:13:13,440
Ye Qiming.

273
00:13:16,080 --> 00:13:17,540
You disappoint me so much.

274
00:13:18,560 --> 00:13:19,320
Despicable.

275
00:13:32,840 --> 00:13:35,240
Xiao Li kept telling me when he got off work just now

276
00:13:35,240 --> 00:13:37,170
that he didn't want to get off work.

277
00:13:37,640 --> 00:13:39,900
His mentor just pushed him out directly.

278
00:13:40,120 --> 00:13:41,360
He had to go home.

279
00:13:41,920 --> 00:13:44,000
His dark circles were almost down to his feet.

280
00:13:44,000 --> 00:13:45,660
How could I not let him go home?

281
00:13:46,200 --> 00:13:48,320
Xiao Li has made progress recently.

282
00:13:48,880 --> 00:13:50,140
You should praise him.

283
00:13:50,520 --> 00:13:53,380
Don't always scold him with a long face. He's young.

284
00:13:53,400 --> 00:13:55,240
All right. What did I say to him?

285
00:13:56,640 --> 00:13:57,240
Shen Feng.

286
00:14:00,760 --> 00:14:01,560
What's wrong?

287
00:14:06,960 --> 00:14:07,600
Nothing.

288
00:14:16,960 --> 00:14:18,090
I'm a little scared.

289
00:14:20,280 --> 00:14:21,140
Scared of what?

290
00:14:23,760 --> 00:14:25,090
When the case is closed,

291
00:14:28,120 --> 00:14:30,180
it'll be time to go back to the office.

292
00:14:32,720 --> 00:14:35,640
Then there will be plenty of people staying up late with you.

293
00:14:35,640 --> 00:14:37,770
Xiao Li should be well-trained by now.

294
00:14:38,920 --> 00:14:40,880
He didn't help much when he came.

295
00:14:44,720 --> 00:14:46,050
Still causing trouble.

296
00:14:50,320 --> 00:14:51,180
Captain Jiang.

297
00:14:54,040 --> 00:14:55,040
Look what this is.

298
00:15:01,880 --> 00:15:02,940
The final payment.

299
00:15:13,440 --> 00:15:14,840
Today, at Lu Yang's door,

300
00:15:15,280 --> 00:15:16,200
I saw Ye Qiming.

301
00:15:39,160 --> 00:15:40,160
Two buns, please.

302
00:15:40,360 --> 00:15:41,040
Meat or vegetable?

303
00:15:41,040 --> 00:15:41,720
One of each.

304
00:15:42,120 --> 00:15:42,640
Okay.

305
00:15:43,040 --> 00:15:44,520
Two more fried dough sticks, boss.

306
00:15:44,520 --> 00:15:46,580
Okay, wait a moment. Coming right up.

307
00:15:46,920 --> 00:15:48,160
Sister Wang, did you hear?

308
00:15:48,160 --> 00:15:49,320
Around here recently,

309
00:15:49,320 --> 00:15:50,650
a college student died.

310
00:15:51,200 --> 00:15:53,520
I wonder when the police will solve the case.

311
00:15:53,520 --> 00:15:55,650
I hope it doesn't affect our business.

312
00:15:59,120 --> 00:16:01,000
The rice tofu is spicy.

313
00:16:28,600 --> 00:16:31,320
Numbing.
